Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.23,0:02:07.85,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,After losing such an utter symbol of its army, Qin lost morale
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.34,0:02:07.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対的な軍の象徴を失った秦は\N武威を失墜し
