Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.85,0:02:14.98,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,and the neighboring states of Zhao, Wei, Han, and Chou began to slowly invade their borders.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.26,0:02:19.94,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,But at this moment, the people of Qin realized
