Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.65,0:02:24.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今こそ 奮い立たねばならぬことを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:27.45,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.16,0:02:27.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏隊長）殺せ！
